{"tid":774933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"食完allmax嘅感受","createTime":"2018-08-10T17:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:23:27.000Z","uid":105396,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0efe5c2e8e52c8f947f22481fe85c87779da6eb9","tid":774933,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"話說近排朋友不停同我講allmax有幾好有幾好<br />\n令我都忍唔住買左一罐試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身對allmax都無咩感覺<br />\n加上每次去bc啲sales都不停叫我買allmax<br />\n攪到我對呢個牌子無咩太大好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼左圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg&h=50128535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左vanilla味<br />\n因為我未試過飲一隻protein的vanilla味係好味同埋vanilla味有折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005615_c7f1901c495bff059d5017c063aa3676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005615_c7f1901c495bff059d5017c063aa3676.jpg&h=7e12f7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開係有少少驚喜，呢個設計。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005639_53c6079d38b14238880f58d6983862e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005639_53c6079d38b14238880f58d6983862e4.jpg&h=8ad557e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一打開陣味好似曲奇雪糕味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005712_3efcc0f3144f621885e27d875fd13266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005712_3efcc0f3144f621885e27d875fd13266.jpg&h=6dd1cb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲色好似精。<br />\n飲落去就係一種曲奇雪糕味，淡淡地，還不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔鐘意太甜嘅朋友建議一試，味道唔會過甜，真係似飲飲品。<br />\n加上一scoop30g有24gprotein嘅數據的確不錯。<br />\n其他味我未試但我想試下佢地個生日蛋糕味。<br />\n以前買左SN桶jumbo gainer嘅vanilla味係死甜，呢隻令我有點對vanilla味同allmax改觀。<br />\n十分我會比八分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0010cd0320c08f27c2d3fb8c2fa3c86d27232923","tid":774933,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說近排朋友不停同我講allmax有幾好有幾好<br />\n令我都忍唔住買左一罐試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身對allmax都無咩感覺<br />\n加上每次去bc啲sales都不停叫我買allmax<br />\n攪到我對呢個牌子無咩太大好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼左圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg&h=50128535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左vanilla味<br />\n因為我未試過飲一隻protein的vanilla味係好味，所以我覺得想試一個牌子有無料就係要飲佢地嘅vanilla<br />\n味。同埋vanilla味有折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005615_c7f1901c495bff059d5017c063aa3676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005615_c7f1901c495bff059d5017c063aa3676.jpg&h=7e12f7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開係有少少驚喜，呢個設計。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005639_53c6079d38b14238880f58d6983862e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005639_53c6079d38b14238880f58d6983862e4.jpg&h=8ad557e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一打開陣味好似曲奇雪糕味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005712_3efcc0f3144f621885e27d875fd13266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005712_3efcc0f3144f621885e27d875fd13266.jpg&h=6dd1cb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲色好似精。<br />\n飲落去就係一種曲奇雪糕味，淡淡地，還不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔鐘意太甜嘅朋友建議一試，味道唔會過甜，真係似飲飲品。<br />\n加上一scoop30g有24gprotein嘅數據的確不錯。<br />\n其他味我未試但我想試下佢地個生日蛋糕味。<br />\n以前買左SN桶jumbo gainer嘅vanilla味係死甜，呢隻令我有點對vanilla味同allmax改觀。<br />\n十分我會比八分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c68081fef61211c0a577b29afd367e0592c5a24c","tid":774933,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說近排朋友不停同我講allmax有幾好有幾好<br />\n令我都忍唔住買左一罐試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身對allmax都無咩感覺<br />\n加上每次去bc啲sales都不停叫我買allmax<br />\n攪到我對呢個牌子無咩太大好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼左圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F005429_62e9bcb1f48e9ae33de6f6f6e8fb62f9.jpg&h=50128535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左vanilla味<br />\n因為我未試過飲一隻protein的vanilla味係好味, <span style=\"color: red;\">所以我覺得想試一個牌子有無料就係要飲佢地嘅vanilla。</span>同埋vanilla味有折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/005615_